  <brief_title>Zirconia and Metal-based Single Crown Posterior Restorations.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Zirconia-based and Metal-based Single Crown Posterior Restorations: 5-year Results of a Randomized Controlled Clinical Study.</official_title>
